Today's journey unveils the power of Ansible rolesâ€”a game-changer in organizing and structuring playbooks. Let's delve into the significance of roles and embark on a practical example!



**Why Roles Bring Harmony:**



ğŸŒ **Modular Automation:** Ansible roles allow us to break down playbooks into reusable, modular components, enhancing organization and clarity.



